ype": "text", "content": "印", "row": 2, "col": 14, "end_col": 17, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "鑑", "row": 2, "col": 17, "end_col": 20, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "・", "row": 2, "col": 21, "end_col": 23, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "印", "row": 2, "col": 24, "end_col": 26, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "鑑", "row": 2, "col": 27, "end_col": 29, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "カ", "row": 2, "col": 30, "end_col": 32, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "ー", "row": 2, "col": 33, "end_col": 35, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "ド", "row": 2, "col": 36, "end_col": 38, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "廃", "row": 2, "col": 39, "end_col": 41, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "止", "row": 2, "col": 42, "end_col": 44, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "届", "row": 2, "col": 45, "end_col": 48, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "書", "row": 2, "col": 48, "end_col": 51, "font_size": 19.6}, {"type": "text", "content": "※", "row": 4, "col": 4, "end_col": 5, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "太枠の中に書いてください。", "row": 4, "col": 6, "end_col": 22, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "（地方）法務局", "row": 5, "col": 9, "end_col": 18, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "支局・出張所", "row": 5, "col": 25, "end_col": 33, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "年", "row": 5, "col": 40, "end_col": 41, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "月", "row": 5, "col": 45, "end_col": 46, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "日", "row": 5, "col": 50, "end_col": 52, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "届出", "row": 5, "col": 52, "end_col": 55, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "印鑑の廃止届出", "row": 6, "col": 6, "end_col": 14, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "印鑑カードの", "row": 7, "col": 6, "end_col": 13, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "印鑑及び印鑑カー廃止届出", "row": 8, "col": 5, "end_col": 11, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "ドの廃止届出", "row": 9, "col": 5, "end_col": 13, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "(いずれかの□にレ印を", "row": 10, "col": 3, "end_col": 15, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "つけてください。)", "row": 11, "col": 3, "end_col": 13, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "（注１）", "row": 13, "col": 3, "end_col": 8, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "商号・名称", "row": 6, "col": 17, "end_col": 24, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "本店・主たる事務所", "row": 8, "col": 16, "end_col": 25, "font_size": 8.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "代表取締役・取締役・代表社員・代表理事・理事・支配人", "row": 9, "col": 25, "end_col": 58, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "(", "row": 10, "col": 26, "end_col": 27, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": ")", "row": 10, "col": 56, "end_col": 57, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "印", "row": 10, "col": 16, "end_col": 17, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "鑑", "row": 11, "col": 16, "end_col": 17, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "提", "row": 12, "col": 16, "end_col": 17, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "出", "row": 13, "col": 16, "end_col": 17, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "者", "row": 14, "col": 16, "end_col": 17, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "資格", "row": 10, "col": 19, "end_col": 24, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "氏名", "row": 11, "col": 19, "end_col": 24, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "生年月日", "row": 14, "col": 18, "end_col": 24, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "大・昭・平・西暦", "row": 14, "col": 26, "end_col": 37, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "年", "row": 14, "col": 43, "end_col": 44, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "月", "row": 14, "col": 48, "end_col": 50, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "日生", "row": 14, "col": 53, "end_col": 56, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "登印記鑑所のに提押出印し欄た", "row": 15, "col": 4, "end_col": 15, "font_size": 8.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "印鑑カード番号", "row": 16, "col": 16, "end_col": 24, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "※カードのみを廃止する場合に、カード廃止の理由", "row": 17, "col": 16, "end_col": 29, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "亡失（なくなった）汚損（著しく汚れた)", "row": 17, "col": 33, "end_col": 45, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "その他", "row": 17, "col": 48, "end_col": 52, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "□にレ印をつけてください。", "row": 18, "col": 17, "end_col": 29, "font_size": 8.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "き損（破損した）", "row": 18, "col": 33, "end_col": 44, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "申請人（注２）", "row": 19, "col": 16, "end_col": 29, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "印鑑提出者本人代理人", "row": 19, "col": 32, "end_col": 48, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "住所", "row": 21, "col": 17, "end_col": 21, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "（印鑑は鮮明に押", "row": 22, "col": 3, "end_col": 15, "font_size": 8.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "印してください。）", "row": 23, "col": 3, "end_col": 15, "font_size": 8.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "フリガナ", "row": 22, "col": 18, "end_col": 21, "font_size": 6.5}, {"type": "text", "content": "氏名", "row": 23, "col": 17, "end_col": 21, "font_size": 12.0}, {"type": "text", "content": "委", "row": 25, "col": 26, "end_col": 27, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "任", "row": 25, "col": 32, "end_col": 33, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "状", "row": 25, "col": 38, "end_col": 39, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "私は、（住所）", "row": 26, "col": 8, "end_col": 15, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "（氏名）", "row": 27, "col": 10, "end_col": 15, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "を代理人と定め、印鑑の廃止届出、印鑑カードの廃止届出、印鑑及び印鑑カード", "row": 28, "col": 7, "end_col": 57, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "の廃止届出、添付書面の原本還付請求及び受領の権限を委任します。", "row": 29, "col": 7, "end_col": 49, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "年", "row": 30, "col": 14, "end_col": 15, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "月", "row": 30, "col": 18, "end_col": 19, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "日", "row": 30, "col": 22, "end_col": 23, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "住所", "row": 31, "col": 8, "end_col": 11, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "登記所に提", "row": 32, "col": 48, "end_col": 55, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "氏名", "row": 32, "col": 8, "end_col": 11, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "印", "row": 32, "col": 43, "end_col": 45, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "市区町村長作成の印鑑証明書は、登記申請書に添付のものを援用する。（注１）", "row": 33, "col": 6, "end_col": 55, "font_size": 10.9}, {"type": "text", "content": "（注１）の印鑑を押印し、作成後３か月以内の市区町村長の証明した印鑑証明書を添付してください。登記所に提出した印鑑を押印してください。この押印ができない場合は、市区町村に登録済み登", "row": 34, "col": 4, "end_col": 57, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "記申請書に添付した印鑑証明書を援用する場合（登記の申請と同時に印鑑を届け出た場合に限る。）", "row": 35, "col": 8, "end_col": 56, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "（注２）は、□にレ印をつけてください。代理人が届け出るときは、代理人の住所・氏名を記載してください。この場合、委任状に所要", "row": 36, "col": 4, "end_col": 57, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "事項を記載し（該当する□にはレ印をつける）、登記所に提出した印鑑を押印してください。", "row": 37, "col": 8, "end_col": 56, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "村長の証明した印鑑証明書を添付してください。この押印ができない場合は、市区町村に登録済みの印鑑を押印し、作成後３か月以内の市区町", "row": 38, "col": 8, "end_col": 57, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "（注３）印鑑カードの交付を受けている場印鑑処理番号受付調査入力校合", "row": 39, "col": 4, "end_col": 59, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "合は、返納してください。この場合には、(注１)の押印及び(注２)の委", "row": 40, "col": 8, "end_col": 27, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "任状は不要です。", "row": 41, "col": 8, "end_col": 18, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "印鑑処理番号", "row": 39, "col": 29, "end_col": 37}, {"type": "text", "content": "受 付", "row": 39, "col": 39, "end_col": 44}, {"type": "text", "content": "調 査", "row": 39, "col": 44, "end_col": 49}, {"type": "text", "content": "入 力", "row": 39, "col": 49, "end_col": 54}, {"type": "text", "content": "校 合", "row": 39, "col": 54, "end_col": 59}, {"type": "text", "content": "（乙号・10)", "row": 42, "col": 3, "end_col": 9, "font_size": 9.8}, {"type": "text", "content": "私は、（住所）", "row": 26, "col": 7, "end_col": 16}, {"type": "border_rect", "row": 24, "end_row": 41, "col": 4, "end_col": 60, "borders": {"top": true, "bottom": true, "left": true, "right": true}}, {"type": "border_rect", "row": 26, "end_row": 26, "col": 7, "end_col": 14, "borders": {"top": true, "bottom": true, "left": true, "right": true}}, {"type": "border_rect", "row": 27, "end_row": 27, "col": 10, "end_col": 14, "borders": {"top": true, "bottom": true, "left": true, "right": true}}]}]